program_description: Social Services Block Grants (SSBG) enables each state or territory to meet the needs of its residents through locally relevant social services. SSBG support programs that allow communities to achieve or maintain economic self-sufficiency to prevent, reduce or eliminate dependency on social services
project_description: Expand substance abuse prevention programming in impacted counties
